<p class="short-reference" data-aid="154070568" id="short_reference1">&#x201C;May 6&#x2013;12. Mosiah 7&#x2013;10,&#x201D; <cite>Come, Follow Me&#x2014;For Home and Church: 2024</cite> (2023)</p>
